# Hardware Components List (BOM)

| # | Component | Specification | Quantity | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Arduino Uno | ATmega328P, 14 digital I/O, 6 analog inputs, 5V/3.3V | 1 | Main microcontroller |
| 2 | Soil Moisture Sensor | Analog output, 3.3V–5V, FC-28 or equivalent | 1 | Reads soil wetness |
| 3 | Relay Module | 5V single-channel, 250VAC/10A or 30VDC/10A | 1 | Switches solenoid valve |
| 4 | Solenoid Valve | 12V DC, normally closed, 1/2 inch | 1 | Controls water flow |
| 5 | HC-05 Bluetooth Module | Serial UART, 2.4GHz, 3.3V logic | 1 | Wireless data & control |
| 6 | Breadboard | 830 tie-points (full size) | 1 | Prototyping |
| 7 | Power Supply | 7–12V DC, min 1A | 1 | Powers Arduino + valve |
| 8 | Resistors | 1kΩ, 2kΩ (for voltage divider) | 2 | HC-05 RX protection |
| 9 | Jumper Wires | Male-to-male, Male-to-female | 1 set | Connections |

---

